{
  "stem": "16395.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The-- not the Germans, I'm sorry, the Russians.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The Russians really bombard-- knew about this camp, and they bombarded the [INAUDIBLE] what the trains were going.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the trains could not go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And this was very late at night, so they said they gonna go with us in the morning for a march.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We're gonna march to Germany.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To Germany.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we were-- we were exhausted.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All day without food and without water, sitting in those barracks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you don't know-- sitting in the--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--train, and not knowing what's going to happen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I went into the barrack, and I probably fell asleep.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Jack and his younger brother and [? anothers-- ?] we didn't hear about Germans, but we heard-- they heard.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was asleep.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I really didn't know it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I took off my shoes, and put them underneath my head, and made from the coat a pillow like I used day after day.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I fell asleep.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they said that somebody said that the Germans ran away, and we don't even have anybody.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he said what will we wait?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Let's go and see it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was like a little bridge from our camp to the place where the Germans lived.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And all three of them went over.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They started going slowly, and they see nobody is there, so they went a little bit further, until they came to the place where the Germans were.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was no one there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They ran away, because the Russians were already so near, so they themselves ran away.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they left, like, three probably empty-- to shoot, what you call it?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Rifles?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Rifles.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They all three took the rifles, and they came back into the camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And everybody picked them up, and everybody was crying.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
